						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Paridhāvin (1492 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>States that the doorway was built in the year <hi rend="bold">Paridhāpi</hi> and that it was the gift (<hi rend="italic">kayiṅkariyam</hi>) of Kōnēridēva-Mahārāja. The details of date <hi rend="italic">viz.,</hi> <hi rend="bold">the 26th of Āvaṇi, Friday, dvitīya, Uttiram</hi> regularly correspond <hi rend="bold">to A.D., 1492 August 24 Friday, f.d.t. ·21; ·49.</hi></p>						

						<p>1 Lines 20—30 are on the side face.</p>						

						</summary>
